author: Google
description:
Here's how we created these iconic '80s looks with #NanoBanana and #Veo3 in #GoogleGemini:

📸 Upload a selfie, tap "Create images" and type "give me an 80s style makeover"
🎥 Want to turn it into a video? Pro and Ultra users can upload their Nano Banana image, tap "Create videos with Veo" from the Tools menu, and get started with a prompt like "the subject turns their head slowly and dramatically to the side"
